========================================================================================
                                Welcome to PhoneBook
========================================================================================

PhoneBook is a web phonebook system which allows you to record and organize contacts.
Supports the following functionality:

    1. Support multiple users
    2. Each user after login is able to record their phone numbers
    3. To organize the numbers in groups / categories
    4. Each entry in the phonebook have standard fields: name, phone, email, address
    5. Ability to create additional (custom) fields
    6. Create category to organize and sort contacts
    7. View all contacts of a category
    8. Viewing and managing contacts / view, update, delete /
    9. Viewing and managing categories / view (also tree view), update, delete /

Created by using PHP Yii - framework